Vibe Payroll Time
Copyright 2026 Kisaes LLC

Vibe Payroll Time is a self-hosted, multi-tenant employee time-tracking
appliance for hourly and shift workers, targeted at CPA firms tracking
their own staff hours (internal use, free) and CPA firms reselling the
appliance to their small-business clients (commercial tier).

